title: Basque separatist ETA has disbanded - reports
text:
Basque separatist ETA has disbanded - reports 6:08pm BST - 01:05
Basque separatist group ETA, which waged a 50-year guerrilla campaign for independence, has completely disbanded, the group said in a letter published on a news site. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
